# MicroFlask

Microflask is microblog platform for everyone.

## Features

* Simple user auth
* CRUD blog post
* Index page shows blog post with pagination
* Build with Python 3, Flask and MongoDB

## Additional Features

* Elasticsearch for search post
* Framework CSS Semantic UI
* Various post type such as link, photo, video, quote, etc.
* User management and administration
* Functional testing
* Acceptance Testing

